{"tid":1477340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］(我知我P牌）香港老師 817 遊行（內有洋蔥）","createTime":"2019-08-16T05:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T11:56:29.000Z","uid":292881,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"855f6d758f071bdf662314c44611da39dbbfdd9d","tid":1477340,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104775110870486/posts/117888199559177/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104775110870486%2Fposts%2F117888199559177%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=38a2b0ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104775110870486/posts/117888199559177/</a><br />\n<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🏫👨🏻&zwj;🏫《我地係香港老師》作出緊急呼籲📣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">教師大遊行（教協主辦）<br />\n日期：8月17日<br />\n時間：上午11時集會、11時半起步<br />\n路線：中環遮打花園至禮賓府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n元朗黑社會無差別攻擊事件，<br />\n警局拉閘拒絕救援。<br />\n至今仍然冇人被起訴<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n警察射傷女救護員右眼球<br />\n可能導致永久失明，<br />\n警察在地鐵站施放催淚彈，<br />\n近距離向示威者開槍<br />\n假扮示威者，<br />\n還拘捕示威者後插贓嫁禍。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭日久，血流得越多，<br />\n難道你到現在還要退縮？<br />\n當權者的冷漠與殘暴，就是要禁聲。<br />\n我們連集會示威的權利也被限制，<br />\n可能有機會在路過時吸入催淚煙，<br />\n有機會行街被警察追打和拘捕。<br />\n既是如此，你還沉默下去嗎？<br />\n<br />\n老師，<br />\n我們在過去兩個經歷過失望和恐懼，<br />\n面對沉重的無力感，<br />\n<br />\n你願不願意站出來，<br />\n與我們同行？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">良知，你還在嗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n守護下一代  為良知發聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n📣教育界 資訊傳播Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=fb6d1115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw</a><br />\n<br />\n🌻我地係香港老師Instagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/wearehongkongteachers?igshid=1af17uuu43z8x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwearehongkongteachers%3Figshid%3D1af17uuu43z8x&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=17f4b247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/wearehongkongteachers?igshid=1af17uuu43z8x</a><br />\n<br />\n❤️我地係香港老師FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WeareHongKongTeachers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWeareHongKongTeachers%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjalzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=be70c7b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WeareHongKongTeachers/</a>"},{"pid":"d2aa147af567e9c1d7179ce1d87253e744f25629","tid":1477340,"uid":167808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://m.facebook.com/logged_out/watch/?video_id=745127305937920&amp;refsrc=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F104775110870486%2Fposts%2F117888199559177%2F&amp;_rdr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flogged_out%2Fwatch%2F%3Fvideo_id%3D745127305937920%26refsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fm.facebook.com%252F104775110870486%252Fposts%252F117888199559177%252F%26_rdr&h=c7a9c31c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4f940b21f947a150716d9f56062519d966b2a1c","tid":1477340,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:55:07.000Z","msg":"817 817 817"},{"pid":"1510a7683eaa872576f8940ce132f121ef3e8bb9","tid":1477340,"uid":220743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:56:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f892c196b1dcf1bfe451b9e166c46b670473e3b","tid":1477340,"uid":147499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-1